ading interface - no reason to be complicated there, very straight-forward.  I liked the influence indicators when building, which helped to find the right combos/locations for buildings.  Heck, looking back over this review, I guess the main problem is there just wasn't enough meat to the game.  I paid $20 to assist production, but didn't get that value from current gameplay.  A bit more depth with future development before release, and I'd probably change my recommendation."
